import axios from "axios"; function Patient_Entry(props){ let {first_name, middle_name, last_name, birth_date, phone_number, email_address, street_address_line1, street_address_line2, city, state, zip_code, photo_path, appointment_date, appointment_time} = props.post; const formattedBirthDate = new Date(birth_date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' }); const formattedApptDate = new Date(appointment_date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric', }); const formattedApptTime = new Date(appointment_time).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { hour: 'numeric', minute: 'numeric' }); return(
  • Last Name: {last_name}
    Middle Initial: {middle_name}
    First Name: {first_name}
    Date of Birth: {formattedBirthDate}
    Phone #: {phone_number}
    Email: {email_address}
    Address1: {street_address_line1}
    Address2: {street_address_line2}
    City: {city}
    State: {state}
    Zip: {zip_code}
    Drivers License Photo: {photo_path}
    Appointment Time: {formattedApptTime}
    Appointment Date: {formattedApptDate}
    • ) } export default Patient_Entry;
